<i>noun</i>: 혼인 [호닌], 혼사 [혼사], 접목 [점목], 장가 [장ː가], 성혼 [성혼], 결혼 [결혼] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>혼인 [호닌]</dt><br>
<dd>marriage; wedding</dd><br>
<dd>남자와 여자가 부부가 되는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a man and woman become a married couple.</dd><br>
<dt>혼사 [혼사]</dt><br>
<dd>marriage; matrimony</dd><br>
<dd>혼인에 관한 일. 또는 혼인하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An affair involving marriage, or an act of getting married.</dd><br>
<dt>접목 [점목]</dt><br>
<dd>1. graft</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 나무에 다른 나무의 가지나 눈을 따다 붙임. 또는 그 나무.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of picking a bud or branch of a plant and uniting it with another plant, or a tree produced by such union.</dd><br>
<dd>2. marriage</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 서로 다른 것들을 잘 어울리게 하여 새로운 것을 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The act of harmonizing different things and create something new.</dd><br>
<dt>장가 [장ː가]</dt><br>
<dd>marriage</dd><br>
<dd>남자가 아내를 맞는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of a man taking a woman as his wife.</dd><br>
<dt>성혼 [성혼]</dt><br>
<dd>wedding; marriage</dd><br>
<dd>결혼이 이루어짐. 또는 결혼을 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A marriage, or getting married.</dd><br>
<dt>결혼 [결혼]</dt><br>
<dd>marriage; wedding; union; matrimony</dd><br>
<dd>남자와 여자가 법적으로 부부가 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>A man and woman become legally a married couple.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>